# BEYOND CODE - Coding Problems and Solutions

Welcome to the **BEYOND CODE** repository! ðŸš€  

This repository contains a collection of challenging coding problems and their solutions, created for the BEYOND CODE competition for first- and second-year Computer Science students.

## About the Competition
BEYOND CODE is an engaging coding challenge designed to:
- Encourage creative problem-solving.
- Strengthen teamwork and collaboration.
- Provide a fun and competitive environment for learning programming concepts.

Participants were tasked with solving a variety of problems, ranging from beginner to advanced levels.

## Repository Structure
- **`Problems/`**: A directory containing all the coding problems presented during the competition.
- **`Solutions/`**: A directory with the solutions to the problems. Each solution is well-documented for educational purposes.

## Highlights
- Written in C++.
- Focused on foundational concepts in programming.
- Real-world challenges that simulate industry-level problem-solving.

